<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Taska - Security Alert</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #dc2626;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            color: #dc2626;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .alert-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fee2e2 0%, #fecaca 100%);
            border: 2px solid #fca5a5;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .alert-box h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #991b1b;
            font-size: 22px;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-box h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #dc2626;
        }
        .info-box ul, .info-box ol {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .info-box li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #dc2626;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #b91c1c;
        }
        .urgent {
            color: #991b1b;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .action-box {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #d97706;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .action-box ol {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .action-box li {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">🚨 Taska - Security Alert</div>
        </div>

        <p>Hello <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>,</p>

        <div class="alert-box">
            <h3>⏰ Security Alert: {{alertType}}</h3>
            <p>We detected unusual or suspicious activity on your Taska account.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>📋 Alert Details:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Alert Type:</strong> {{alertType}}</li>
                <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</li>
                <li><strong>Alert Time:</strong> {{alertTime}}</li>
                <li><strong>Details:</strong> {{details}}</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center;" class="urgent">⚠️ This requires your immediate attention!</p>

        <div class="action-box">
            <strong style="color: #92400e;">Take Action Now:</strong>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Change your password immediately</strong> with a new, strong password</li>
                <li><strong>Enable two-factor authentication</strong> if not already enabled</li>
                <li><strong>Review your recent account activity</strong> for any unauthorized changes</li>
                <li><strong>Contact our security team</strong> if you don't recognize this activity</li>
                <li><strong>Check your connected devices</strong> and log out from unknown devices</li>
            </ol>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="https://taska-rho.vercel.app/security" class="btn">Secure My Account Now</a>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
            <h3>🔐 Additional Security Measures:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>✅ Use a strong, 12+ character password</li>
                <li>✅ Enable two-factor authentication</li>
                <li>✅ Monitor your account regularly</li>
                <li>✅ Review connected apps and devices</li>
                <li>✅ Report any suspicious activity immediately</li>
                <li>✅ Update your recovery email and phone</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #fee2e2; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626;">
            <p class="urgent" style="margin-top: 0;">⚠️ Didn't perform this action?</p>
            <ul style="margin: 10px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Contact our security team <strong>immediately</strong></li>
                <li>Change your password right away</li>
                <li>Monitor your financial accounts</li>
                <li>Check for any unauthorized changes to your tasks or profile</li>
                <li>Consider reviewing your connected integrations</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p class="urgent">This is an automated security alert from Taska.</p>
            <p>For security concerns, contact our team immediately: support@taska.app</p>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Taska. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>🚀 Smart Task Management - Protecting Your Data</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 